HEADWORD: bumpkinly
<hw>bump"kin*ly</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>unsophisticated in a manner
resembling a lifelong resident of rural areas; <as>as,
<ex>bumpkinly</ex> country boys</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hick, rustic, unsophisticated.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bumptious</ent>⟦br⟧
